quran[3]{c,v,t,f}:
  2,13,"Soni naga asalilidwemo kuti: “Kulupililani yatite pakulupilila ŵandu ŵane.” Akasatiji: “Ana tukulupilile yatite pakulupilila ŵawawate?” Manyililani yanti ŵanganyao chisimu chene niŵali ŵakuwawata, nambo ngakupata kumanyilila."
  2,14,"Soni naga asimene ni aŵala ŵakulupilile, akasatiji: “Tukulupilile,” nambo pati apite pa kasyepela ku mashetani gajao, akasatiji: “Chisimu uwwe tulinamwe, uwwetu tukuŵa tuli nkwatenda chipongwe.”"
  2,15,"Allah chachalipila pa chipongwe chaocho, ni chiŵalechelele nkusokonechela mwaomo achiyumbagayumbaga."